name: Pagod na aq
description:
Pagod na aq (I am tired) by Jarrett Cross | 2021 | VQGAN + CLIP, Photomanipulation.

Aug. 19,2021
I'm tired. The past days has really been tiring even if I'm just sitting in front of my laptop. Work is piling up. I'm slowly getting tired socialising even if I need it. Anxiety takes over, making me overwhelmed and troubled to start working. But despite these challenges, good things still happen. And I am still thankful. Reminding myself that it's okay to feel tired. Rest. Get back when you can.
